\v 19 An³ Pablo ntsa⁴ qui³squi³-nia³, an³ cˀoe³chja¹³. A³li²coi³ cˀoa⁴xin¹-le²³ nca³ nqui²sa⁴ tse³ qui³tjen⁴-li² cjoa⁴vi³jna³chon³-li⁴ xi³ tˀa³tsˀan⁴.  
\v 20 Jaon³, ntsˀe³, ca²ta³ma³tsjoa³ya³-na³ tˀa³tsi⁴ nca³ ti³yo³coa⁴² Nai³-na¹. Ti⁴qui³njen³nchˀan¹yai³ ni⁴ma⁴-na⁴ nca³ ti³yo³coa⁴² Nai³-na¹.  
